videos.description: Lamar Jackson continues his impressive play, hitting Jaylen Smith for a 61-yard pick up to get Louisville to the Syracuse six yard line.
videos.headline: Big play has Louisville knocking on the door again

videos.description: After accounting for eight touchdowns last week, and already having a passing touchdown today, Lamar Jackson scores on his own with a seven yard run to make it 14-0 Louisville in less than three minutes.
videos.headline: Jackson can't stop scoring TDs for Louisville

videos.description: After starting the game throwing a 72-yard touchdown, Lamar Jackson takes it himself for a 72-yard touchdown run, his second rushing score of the game to make it 21-0 Louisville.
